### December 22nd, 2017 ###
Here are the Blockmason Dev Updates for December 22nd:

#### Lndr Updates ####

1. The updated UX designs are completed and implementation has begun.

2. Push notifications have been added for pending transactions and will be released to testers soon.

3. Server-side implementation of Eth debt settlement has started, and client integration will start after the UX redesign is complete.
